lead_paragraph: Wissam Ben Yedder's first Champions League goal gave Sevilla a 1-0 win over Olympique Lyon on Tuesday and put them level on points with Juventus at the top of Group H.

headline.print_headline: Ben Yedder Gives Sevilla 1-0 Champions League Win Over Lyon
